ghts planning.  Please note that the area of TMT contains the following subsections: Information Technology, Media, Telecommunications.', 1, 1, 'Law Firm; Practice Group', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 3939, '', '', NULL, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
