(42, 'Best Lawyers', 'Best Lawyers in America', 2015, 'Best Lawyers is the oldest and most respected peer-review publication in the legal profession. A listing in Best Lawyers is widely regarded by both clients and legal professionals as a significant honor, conferred on a lawyer by his or her peers. For more than three decades, Best Lawyers lists have earned the respect of the profession, the media, and the public, as the most reliable, unbiased source of legal referrals anywhere. \nOnline: https://www.bestlawyers.com/Admin/Nomination.aspx\nFor the 2014 (20th) Edition of The Best Lawyers in America, 637 lawyers in the Connecticut region listed in Best Lawyers were contacted by telephone, email, and/or fax. Each one received a ballot tailored to his or her legal specialty and location. Of that group, 489 ballots were returned (77%). The total pool of candidates included 647 previously-listed Connecticut lawyers and 437 new nominees. Overall, 49,308 votes were cast.', '10-Apr-15', 1, 1, '', '', 'USA', 'North America', '', '', 'Annual', '', '', '', 'Individual', '', '2015', '', 'http://www.bestlawyers.com/', ''),
