(82, 'Chambers & Partners', 'Intellectual Property', 2016, 'The Chambers Guides have been ranking the best law firms and lawyers since 1990, and now cover 185 jurisdictions throughout the world.Intellectual Property covers disputes related to patent, copyright and trademark infringement. Litigation concerning trade secrets also features. We also feature related issues such as licensing and IP commercialisation (US patent prosecution).  This section includes Copyrights. Please include any Copyrights work as part of the main Intellectual Property submission, Any relevant clients should also be part of the list of 10 Intellectual Property referees.', '1-Jan-16', 1, 1, '', '', 'Colombia', 'South America', 'Intellectual Property', 'Competition', 'Annual', '', '', '', 'Law Firm; Practice Group', '', '', 'http://www.chambersandpartners.com/global-practice-area-definitions', 'http://www.chambersandpartners.com/', ''),
