(208, 'Chambers & Partners', 'Insurance (International Firms)', 2016, 'The Chambers Guides have been ranking the best law firms and lawyers since 1990, and now cover 185 jurisdictions throughout the world.Insurance includes both contentious and non-contentious insurance and reinsurance matters. On the contentious side, we feature coverage claims litigation, broker`s negligence and both `facultative` and `treaty` reinsurance disputes. There is also a element of professional negligence issues arising from insurance disputes. On the non-contentious side, we include all forms of M&A, capital raisings, demutualisations and other regulatory issues.     Please note that the area of Insurance includes the following subsections: Insurance: Dispute Resolution.    Please include contentious and non-contentious FSR work in one submission', '29-Feb-16', 1, 1, '', '', 'China', 'Asia', 'Insurance', '', 'Annual', '', '', '', 'Law Firm; Practice Group', '', '', '', '', ''),
