(591, 'Chambers & Partners ', 'Labour & Employment', 2015, 'The Chambers Guides have been ranking the best law firms and lawyers since 1990, and now cover 185 jurisdictions throughout the world.Covers both contentious and non-contentious employment matters relating to day-to-day business issues as well as mergers and takeovers. Includes employment litigation related to sex, race, age discrimination. In the USA, this also includes class action suits, and the avoidance of class action certification. Includes workforce redundancies and employment issues related to the merger of two companies. Lawyers also advise on the writing of policy handbooks, HR training and corporate governance for major corporates.', '2-Nov-15', 1, 1, '', '', 'Guatemala', 'North America', 'Employment Law', '', 'Annual', 'Carlota GarciaPatel', '', '4420 7778 1643', 'Law Firm; Practice Group', '', '', 'http://www.chambersandpartners.com/global-practice-area-definitions', 'http://www.chambersandpartners.com/', ''),
(592, 'Chambers & Partners ', 'Tax', 2015, 'The Chambers Guides have been ranking the best law firms and lawyers since 1990, and now cover 185 jurisdictions throughout the world.Tax covers a broad range of matters on both the contentious and non-contentious side. Non-contentious matters include M&A transactions and equity raising issues both at domestically and abroad, as well as tax advisory work on behalf of corporate clients. Financing and investment management are other key non-contentious tax issues. On the contentious side, disputes with public authorities in the form of litigation, appeals and tribunals are included. In the UK, indirect tax matters, including such duties as VAT and stamp duty, are also covered.   Please note that the area of Tax Law contains the following subsections: Consultants.', '2-Nov-15', 1, 1, '', '', 'Guatemala', 'North America', 'Tax', '', 'Annual', 'Carlota GarciaPatel', '', '4420 7778 1643', 'Law Firm; Practice Group', '', '', 'http://www.chambersandpartners.com/global-practice-area-definitions', 'http://www.chambersandpartners.com/', ''),
(593, 'Chambers & Partners ', 'Corporate/M&A', 2015, 'The Chambers Guides have been ranking the best law firms and lawyers since 1990, and now cover 185 jurisdictions throughout the worldChambers'' coverage of Competition and Antitrust covers the body of laws that prohibits anti-competitive behaviour (monopoly) and unfair business practices. This includes practices that hurt business, consumers, or both, or that generally violate standards of ethical behaviour. Antitrust litigation and M&A-related competition work, such as merger control are also covered by this section.  This section pertains to international firms handling India work from outside the jurisdiction', '1-Dec-15', 1, 1, '', '', 'Guatemala', 'North America', 'Corporate; M&A', '', 'Annual', 'Carlota GarciaPatel', '', '4420 7778 1643', 'Law Firm; Practice Group', '', '', 'http://www.chambersandpartners.com/global-practice-area-definitions', 'http://www.chambersandpartners.com/', ''),
