(685, 'Law 360', ' California Powerhouses', 2015, 'Law360 is looking to profile firms with a strong regional presence. Submissions must be no\nmore than 1,500 words, and an accurate word count must be included. Your submission\nshould include the number of attorneys working in the state (use head count, not full-time\nequivalent); a list of the offices the firm has in the state; and a detailed description of significant\nlitigation wins, transactions or projects worked on in the state from March 1, 2014, to March 1,\n2015. Submission forms should be titled “Region - Firm Name.” (Example: Texas - Law Firm.) Send\nsubmission forms to editor@law360.com with the email subject line, “Regional Powerhouse:\nFirm Name.” You may attach multiple submissions to one e-mail.', '1-Apr-15', 1, 1, '', 'CA', 'USA', 'US West', '', '', 'Annual', '', 'editor@law360.com', '646-783-7100 ext 3', 'Law Firm', '', '2014', 'https://www.law360.com/Law360-2015-Editorial-Calendar.pdf', 'https://www.law360.com/', 'subscribed'),
